<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to SIU</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0; 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 80%;
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .display-4 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: red;
        }

        .school-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 80%;
            max-width: 1300px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .info-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .decorative-line {
            border-top: 2px solid #007bff;
            margin: 40px auto;
            max-width: 100px;
        }

        .service {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .service-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .service-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .service-description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to SIU</h1>
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/ff/Mat_tien_SIU.jpg/1200px-Mat_tien_SIU.jpg" alt="School Image" class="school-image">
        <p class="info-text">Explore our programs, faculty, and campus life to discover why SIU is the perfect place for your academic journey.</p>
        <hr class="decorative-line">
        <div class="service">
            <i class="fas fa-book-open service-icon"></i>
            <h2 class="service-title">Academic Programs</h2>
            <p class="service-description">Discover our wide range of academic programs designed to meet the diverse needs and interests of our students.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service">
            <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher service-icon"></i>
            <h2 class="service-title">Experienced Faculty</h2>
            <p class="service-description">Learn from our team of experienced faculty members who are dedicated to providing quality education and mentorship.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service">
            <i class="fas fa-university service-icon"></i>
            <h2 class="service-title">Campus Life</h2>
            <p class="service-description">Immerse yourself in our vibrant campus community filled with clubs, events, and activities to enhance your college experience.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
